The documents provided state that "Best Buddies International is a nonprofit 501(c)(3) organization dedicated to establishing a global volunteer movement that creates opportunities for one-to-one friendships, integrated employment, leadership development, and inclusive living for individuals with intellectual and developmental disabilities (IDD)." They also mention that it was founded in 1989 by Anthony K. Shriver, which supports the statement "Best Buddies International was founded in 1989."
